narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes! If you want to enrich your vietnamese absolutely.There's so much flexibility.

You must be disciplined in setting up meeting times with Prof Quang. He is usually very available but will not regularly press you to come meet with him.If you go too long without meeting, it may be hard to stay on-track with your project. Prof Quang is great with explaining grammar and clarifying translations.
